data.title: Me & Terry Farrell (aka Lt. Jadzia Dax)
data.meta_description: Was flagged down by her and her husband in Marylebone High Street, London, and as soon as she was in the cab I knew who she was straight away.  Unfortunately I could only remember her character name, not her real name, but she was as stunning as I remember from the series - what a touch - I wanted to put my arm around her waste, but that wouldn't have been very appropriate (plus her husband was the one taking the photo)
